Titles.eng: Girls und Panzer das Finale: Part  I
Titles.jpn: ガールズ&パンツァー 最終章 第1話

Summaries.eng: Victory over the battle with university selection team who survived the school and finally had a peaceful winter day Members of Oarai girls' school tank champion team. Minor changes began, as students graduated from third graders, the student council was reelected and the new executive department started. One day, the riot which fell on top of them. In order to confront the challenge that appeared again, the tank road team will restart.
